    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 债券可能在股价上涨 390% 后转换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/microstrategy-bonds-likely-to-convert-after-390-share-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币投资者 MicroStrategy Inc. 陷入了困境，因为比特币最近的上涨不仅提振了其股价，还提振了其可转换债券。由于再融资成本上升了 280%，投资者正准备等待该公司将债券转换为股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/microstrategy-bonds-likely-to-convert-after-390-share-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 17:49:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
